{"tid":2066305,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］賣廣告賣到要TVB親自教人Del Comment？","createTime":"2020-06-16T07:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T01:29:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b19da295da20db7a757970f609e3e16b67e3b390","tid":2066305,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-NGiOns68WyMmV_zbsQQefZA1yA=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/UA73JHUTOWXF7LQW7WFTUV2IHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-NGiOns68WyMmV_zbsQQefZA1yA%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FUA73JHUTOWXF7LQW7WFTUV2IHA.jpg&h=e01cdd49&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<strong>TLDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳洲膚潤康藥業</span>(15 Jun)岩岩刪走大量留言，又唔比人upload圖片</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/fuyunhon/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Ffuyunhon%2Fposts%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=6f48c3ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/fuyunhon/posts/</a><br />\n<br />\n=======================================================<br />\n話說響上年年尾，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB將網民既良心消費行動定性為「社交媒體騷擾」，於是就開咗個講座教啲廣告商點樣對付網民</span></strong>，例如set過濾字眼，篩走曬「抵制」、「CCTVB」、「罷買」及「助紂為虐」等等留言，不愧係公關專家，自己做得差唔去諗點樣改善，反而教人點樣打擊批評意見，TVB真係憑住實力變成一間無人睇既電視台<br />\n<br />\n又等我響呢度<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歸納下Page Admin通常會用咩手法打壓異見，同埋可以點樣突破限制</span></strong>啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. 洗Post，出大量既新帖文將嬲嬲洗走</strong></span><br />\n應對：派埋嬲比icon、cover photo，勤力啲留言<br />\n不過如果係出帖頻率極高，例如證券行page會日日po財經新經、超市便利店page會日日po優惠，呢啲就要量力而為，我唔想你花完一日精力狂派嬲，之後厭惡咗呢個活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典例子：美味假期旅行社表示唔再落TVB廣告，跟住又縮沙，網民不忿對方出爾反爾，於是旅行社出咗大量「旅行回顧」post推走曬啲留言<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. 設定過濾字眼</strong></span><br />\n如果你輸入關鍵字例如「CCTVB」、「抵制」，該留言就會被隱藏<br />\n應對：使用個性化既留言、字眼，例如「紅媒」、「偏頗電視台」、「ＴＶＢ」代替TVB，中文既野係千變萬化，相信難你地唔到<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QvEQOh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QvEQOh.jpg&h=bcb9eacf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有時按「全部留言」會出返手足啲留言，有時就hide forever</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3. 刪留言</strong></span><br />\n應對：唯有勤力啲留言，而且就算刪到留言，都刪唔到嬲嬲嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n經典例子：雙飛人，page admin扮到好親民咁，一邊同網民有講有笑，一邊刪曬批評意見<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mi61jJn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMi61jJn.jpg&h=70734b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">望吓啲留言去曬邊</span> <br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">雙飛人FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/peppermintcure/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fpeppermintcure%2Fposts&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=29193daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/peppermintcure/posts</a></span></em></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>4. 唔比上載圖片</strong></span><br />\n好多手足留言之餘都會上載埋幅靚靚圖片，例如佐證點解TVB新聞係偏頗、說以TVB賣廣告既利弊，好多時廣告商一見到網民咁做就會封鎖up圖功能<br />\n<br />\n應對：post張圖既link上去就得，post啲有圖既新聞link更佳<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hi8SrkL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhi8SrkL.jpg&h=c29d93d0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bless FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/bless.juices/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fbless.juices%2Fposts&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=f37569bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/bless.juices/posts</a></span></em></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>5. 請打手(有待商榷)</strong></span><br />\n高度懷疑某啲page係會請打手洗版，同TVB戰士抗衡，有啲會直接開罵戰，有啲會覆香討式留言(好正呀、支持，或者齋post sticker)，有啲就唔知點解出post幾分鐘就有大量like<br />\n<br />\n此外，某啲page間唔中就會出抽獎活動，叫人like同share，但某啲ac入面係咩都無，或者全部都係share廣告商既帖文<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLzFAkK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLzFAkK.jpg&h=e3b4a106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實係咪會有師奶日日無野做剩係參加唔同公司活動?<br />\n<em>嘉頓FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gardenhongkong/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgardenhongkong%2Fposts&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=857a14fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gardenhongkong/posts</a></em></span></div><br />\n不過，我都唔排除有藍絲會自發同手足對抗既，所以呢個point有待商椎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6PFAh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6PFAh2.jpg&h=57cc9302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我見有啲手足會逐個sticker派嬲，不過對家係特登洗版、挑機，建議可以唔洗理呢類留言，盞攰親自己</span><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">OK便利店 FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/circlekhongkong/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fcirclekhongkong%2Fposts&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=6e05680f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/circlekhongkong/posts</a></span></em></div> <br />\n<br />\n最後都要重申，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地支持自由經濟，我地同意廣告商有賣廣告既自由，但顧客都有選擇買同唔買既自由，我地只會抵制無良商戶，但唔會威脅佢地</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#你有權利賣廣告我地有能力抵制你<br />\n#犯法野我地唔做嫁<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報《網民炸爆廣告商 腳軟TVB教客戶鎖帖兼報警》<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>原文：<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191101/MDRESXLHPDTNK56CBWAVD5CBGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191101%2FMDRESXLHPDTNK56CBWAVD5CBGE%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=6e5ed4cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191101%2FMDRESXLHPDTNK56CBWAVD5CBGE%2F&h=5f771e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191101/MDRESXLHPDTNK56CBWAVD5CBGE/</a><br />\n\t</em></span>"},{"pid":"e7b8e8e27858627ff7cc39817bcecc2969175f01","tid":2066305,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<br />\n【刪一貼百】賣廣告賣到要TVB親自教人Del Comment？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2066200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2066200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61018fc26b9209fb1f182db40e717bf6c0b1f495","tid":2066305,"uid":199834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ba6194468983d8f1cf13b079bf79b617508fa2","tid":2066305,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b11769010ba281fce4c70b24d088b6c3707b2fc","tid":2066305,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}